org.jaudiotagger.audio.mp3
Class MPEGFrameHeader

java.lang.Object
  org.jaudiotagger.audio.mp3.MPEGFrameHeader

public class MPEGFrameHeader
extends java.lang.Object

Represents a MPEGFrameHeader, an MP3 is made up of a number of frames each frame starts witha four byte frame header.
